phrs.translation: 鰕虎鱼, 虾虎鱼, 鰕虎鱼类

sentences.sentence: Has some of the most beautiful freshwater fishes found anywhere, including gobies, gudgeons and rainbow fish.
sentences.translation: 新几内亚拥有一些最漂亮的淡水鱼，而且这些鱼随处可见。包括暇虎鱼，白杨鱼以及彩虹鱼。
